{"tid":1838762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［24.01.2020 14:36］ 香港迪士尼樂園運作正常","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:47:29.000Z","uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d931decf221a4310b609c83ed5fe6d96414c8541","tid":1838762,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"上海迪士尼樂園宣布，明日起關閉，直至另行通知。度假區會同政府部門緊密溝通，決定重開日期，並會協助購買了門票及預訂酒店的旅客，辦理退款手續。<br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園度假區發言人說，香港迪士尼樂園運作正常，會繼續加強清潔及採取額外預防措施，包括在高使用量的設施，加密清潔次數，亦在度假區不同位置額外增設潔手液裝置；演藝人員如有需要可戴口罩。樂園會密切留意最新疫情，並與相關政府部門保持緊密聯繫，繼續採取合適的預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255535&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1255535%26csid%3D261_341&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=5782fdf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1255535&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9da6234f7e1278135ba1c8ad797c2e0bc8716820","tid":1838762,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"}]}